{"tid":2507212,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「黑警老豆」supper moment上開心大綜藝，真係樂壇之恥","createTime":"2021-04-28T00:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T01:06:24.000Z","uid":43785,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae89bfd6ca473559cf3bdd5227bf663bc142b15","tid":2507212,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:51:15.000Z","msg":"supper moment，曾經係年青人最喜歡嘅樂隊，唱埋啲罐頭歌，攞個最喜愛組合。不過近年真係食屎啦<br />\n<br />\n唱撚埋啲廢歌。荼毒青少年都算。<br />\n前年香港打撚到仆街，自己粒聲唔出。<br />\n靠老豆做黑警關係直接上大陸接SHOW搵錢。<br />\n仲成日搵打手上連登吹奏佢係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心慳D啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2kV14X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2kV14X.jpg&h=b7d8e7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦，有viu頒獎禮你唔上，原來係嫌人得4點收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢要上CCTVB上開心大綜藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淪落到同胡楓合唱。仲要唱完一首又一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我真係屌你老母啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXUzydd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXUzydd.jpg&h=22f513d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前仲話夠真，敢言見稱，依家睇過？？<br />\n真係墮落到仆街，樂壇之恥。<br />\n定係從來都冇變過，<br />\nsupper moment一直支持黑警打後生仔？<br />\n支持CCTVB？支持共產黨？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tYd1dbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtYd1dbB.jpg&h=2bf3be0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HFe0tKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHFe0tKX.jpg&h=870b1326&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"021abe90f1836192a92426918a2b84a4e396dfaf","tid":2507212,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:51:49.000Z","msg":"鳩sir老豆？"},{"pid":"6b2e734662c66e4bf176ccbb6057bcff7fc33367","tid":2507212,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仲要主動請打手做埋啲戇鳩野<br />\n<br />\nSupper moment 主動宣傳 viutv chill club，但唔宣傳 tvb 開心大綜藝，大家心照啦 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2504060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2504060</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n調撚轉嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbef6d6157c9b23dd7cdb7061c8a23603f3051ce","tid":2507212,"uid":325855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:52:09.000Z","msg":"Good morning sir起身返工？"},{"pid":"034d019af8ad6414695ef3736bd129f68808e353","tid":2507212,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:52:48.000Z","msg":"無盡？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65e2980dabeb25edfa147800e1b1a089af389cb","tid":2507212,"uid":391029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"Yes sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9693c3b3504b7ee30a0cddaf30b5905c8bcdc002","tid":2507212,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:53:34.000Z","msg":"你"},{"pid":"0c219c664823d717d0b9a321449e319ccc05a148","tid":2507212,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:54:05.000Z","msg":"你點恥的"},{"pid":"aa86e79c037d733ef4347c950f8b13ea5f76f97f","tid":2507212,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"你點sup的"},{"pid":"dfad07393b54996cde28aac126efeb7d3a0f1d44","tid":2507212,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:55:25.000Z","msg":"侮辱沙燕之歌"},{"pid":"b09f27d7bf621d8a081e3a2abe9b185dc536942f","tid":2507212,"uid":189220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:55:31.000Z","msg":"viu頒獎禮佢有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf08f8827480baa3a07939379fe863f165f6d18","tid":2507212,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:57:19.000Z","msg":"Supper好黃架😆😆😆"},{"pid":"e29bb70f24a646a4a210a53024f6a2e3d3c80632","tid":2507212,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"去老人台唱埋啲20+年前以上嘅舊歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b82d95d82e9f008ba7eda031527366c29ec101","tid":2507212,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"034d019af8ad6414695ef3736bd129f68808e353","tid":2507212,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:52:48.000Z","msg":"無盡？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"呢隊嘢仲有好多人幫佢兜，話老豆唔係自己可以選擇。<br />\n<br />\n但係上CCTVB，可以自己選擇啦掛？<br />\n支持黃定藍可以自己選擇啦掛？<br />\n平時敢言見稱，香港人俾黑警打到仆街，可以選擇出聲啦啩？<br />\n<br />\n香港人抗爭打到咁，仲有心情返大陸搵人民幣接SHOW？<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦，Supper Moment"},{"pid":"e4cda39447af9fbf6bb0042ddee8f20683e4a3a6","tid":2507212,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"Supper Moment曾經連續四年獲得由樂迷投選的叱咤樂壇我最喜愛組合獎，一度被年輕人追捧，更被譽為繼Beyond後的神級香港樂隊，但這兩年非常低調，甚至被指「染紅」。剛過去的星期日，SM四子現身TVB《開心大綜藝》節目擔任嘉賓，更與89歲胡楓（修哥）Jam歌，事後卻在社交網絕口不提，引來網民狠批，更嘲諷他們已變成「修哥Moment」，經已「踏上這無綫旅途」<br />\n<br />\nSupper Moment曾經是香港一眾年輕人的偶像，大賣貼地及搖滾不死精神，但近年世界變了樣，他們變得低調，一改過去的形象，亦引發兩批網民經常在SM社交網上罵戰。還以為事件告一段落，但<span class=\"orange\">最近SM入選「Chill Club頒獎禮」卻缺席頒獎禮，原來因為要出席TVB節目！剛剛星期日晚上的《開心大綜藝》，就看到SM與修哥Jam歌，化身「修哥Moment」。</span><br />\n<br />\n節目中，Supper Moment與修哥合唱老歌〈舊歡如夢〉、〈我的親愛〉及〈紅日〉，更有小朋友伴舞，與平日搖滾形象大變，網民深感SM淪落至此，感到非常失望，衝入社交網留言。有趣是，無論FB及IG，Supper Moment都沒有分享當晚在TVB的任何相片及片段，難怪有網民留言指：「上得TVB，但IG淨係放Chill Club？上TVB好唔見得光咩？」、「上TVB做音樂都冇所謂，做小丑就算吧啦」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WjW6poU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjW6poU.jpg&h=c3bd6d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據說，修哥將於6月在紅館舉行「修哥共你70載 胡楓約你開心派對2021」，他在節目後更宣佈請到SM做表演嘉賓，主辦機構亦在FB專頁表示，「修哥活力澎湃與Supper Moment又唱又跳，四子將會出席6月份做演唱會嘉賓」。於是，有網民揶揄他們：「係咪搵TBB藝人扮佢哋做組合去演唱會」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ph8sThb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fph8sThb.jpg&h=5b4ed8ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9593688962daba584b0bcf810995e7db8f376fb","tid":2507212,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09f27d7bf621d8a081e3a2abe9b185dc536942f","tid":2507212,"uid":189220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:55:31.000Z","msg":"viu頒獎禮佢有去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"SM缺席頒獎禮兼捧蛋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210427/KF6CIALNSVAIVFWH6TIPIMXWTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210427%2FKF6CIALNSVAIVFWH6TIPIMXWTU%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0tOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=014a7b82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210427%2FKF6CIALNSVAIVFWH6TIPIMXWTU%2F&h=0a312ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210427/KF6CIALNSVAIVFWH6TIPIMXWTU/</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"c9b82d95d82e9f008ba7eda031527366c29ec101","tid":2507212,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"呢隊嘢仲有好多人幫佢兜，話老豆唔係自己可以選擇。<br />\n<br />\n但係上CCTVB，可以自己選擇啦掛？<br />\n支持黃定藍可以自己選擇啦掛？<br />\n平時敢言見稱，香港人俾黑警打到仆街，可以選擇出聲啦啩？<br />\n<br />\n香港人抗爭打到咁，仲有心情返大陸搵人民幣接SHOW？<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦，Supper Moment"}}